@startuml CU12_Component
!include ../_shared/global_style.iuml

title CU-12 — Consultar grafo cognitivo: Diagrama de Componentes
note as N1
    Django is NOT involved in CU-12.
    Angular calls AxiomEngine directly on port 8080.
end note

package "Angular SPA (port 4200)" {
    component [CognitiveGraphComponent] as CGComp
    component [HttpClient] as Http
    component [Cytoscape.js / D3 Renderer] as Renderer
}

package "AxiomEngine (Go + Fiber, port 8080)" {
    component [handlers.go\nHTTP handler registration] as Handlers
    component [graph/memory.go\ngraph classification logic] as GraphMem
    component [BAML Orchestrator] as BAML
}

cloud "AWS Bedrock" {
    component [Amazon Nova Micro] as LLM
}

CGComp --> Http : build request
Http --> Handlers : GET /api/v1/tutor/student/:student_id/\ncognitive-graph?topics=...
Handlers --> GraphMem : ClassifyCognitiveGraph()
GraphMem --> BAML : structured prompts
BAML --> LLM : parallel fan-out
LLM --> BAML : classification responses
BAML --> GraphMem : merged results
GraphMem --> Handlers : { nodes[], edges[] }
Handlers --> Http : HTTP 200 JSON
Http --> CGComp : { nodes[], edges[] }
CGComp --> Renderer : render graph

note right of Handlers
    Resilience:
    - Circuit breaker (3 failures → open, 15s half-open)
    - Rate limiter (50 req/min/IP)
end note

@enduml
